Class NodeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • comingle.comms.directory.NodeInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class NodeInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A record class containing information on a particular node. A BaseDirectory essentially maintains a list of NodeInfo in each participating node's directory.
    Author:
    Edmund S.L. Lam
